Time":"2019-10-21T03:58:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Vwm279.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Vwm279.jpg&h=20411ccc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rqipgtb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRqipgtb.jpg&h=b3da3095&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n文宣圖<br />\n<br />\n原圖pdf:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1qHCZ1DiHGUgnFprEJBMfBTvnS-60RLE8/view?usp=drivesdk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1qHCZ1DiHGUgnFprEJBMfBTvnS-60RLE8%2Fview%3Fusp%3Ddrivesdk&d=g2FbBnZIPvId2LkE7nNtjawvV4D0jUJVCqNn8v1PCJE%3D&h=fdd0e32d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1qHCZ1DiHGUgnFprEJBMfBTvnS-60RLE8/view?usp=drivesdk</a><br />\n<br />\nFB：阿門<br />\nIG ： pieceofpaper_pq"},{"pid":"736810071809c74e7c7d521eb1d2578c9a7b0481","tid":1665829,"uid":315604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bfd421cc8c0d3b29c2ea296a74785a3be19903a","tid":1665829,"uid":315604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T03:58:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Vwm279.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Vwm279.jpg&h=20411ccc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rqipgtb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRqipgtb.jpg&h=b3da3095&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n文宣圖<br />\n<br />\n原圖pdf:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1qHCZ1DiHGUgnFprEJBMfBTvnS-60RLE8/view?usp=drivesdk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1qHCZ1DiHGUgnFprEJBMfBTvnS-60RLE8%2Fview%3Fusp%3Ddrivesdk&d=g2FbBnZIPvId2LkE7nNtjawvV4D0jUJVCqNn8v1PCJE%3D&h=fdd0e32d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1qHCZ1DiHGUgnFprEJBMfBTvnS-60RLE8/view?usp=drivesdk</a><br />\n<br />\nFB：阿門<br />\nIG ： pieceofpaper_pq"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T03:58:23.000Z","msg":"推"}]}